          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/7512648.Leta_Hong_Fincher"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1395715277p3/7512648.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/7512648.Leta_Hong_Fincher">Leta Hong Fincher
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
